# Internal Critique

## Fatal Flaws (fix before sharing)
- Contribution unclear in 2 sentences
- Missing key baselines
- No statistical significance (single run)
- Claims not supported by results
- Overclaiming "state-of-the-art"

## Major Weaknesses
- No ablation study
- Single narrow dataset
- Missing limitations section
- Outdated related work

## Reviewer Simulation
Write in reviewer voice:
"The authors claim X but only demonstrate Y. Missing baseline Z..."

Then write rebuttal response:
"We thank the reviewer. We will add Z..."

## Output
Fatal flaws → Major weaknesses → Minor issues → Priority fixes (top 3)
